[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0541","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0541.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0326","title":"HP HP-UX mediainit 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 mediainit 媒体设备初始化程序存在安全漏洞。该程序用于初始化磁带机等存储设备，但由于对输入参数缺乏充分验证，本地攻击者可利用该缺陷，通过向 mediainit 程序传递特制参数触发漏洞，导致系统机密信息部分泄露、系统数据被部分篡改或服务部分不可用。此漏洞为本地利用，无需额外认证，攻击复杂度低，影响 HP-UX 系统多个版本，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。HP 已通过安全公告 HPSBUX9710-071 提供修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0326"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.543","remediation":"立即应用 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9710-071 提供的官方补丁。如无法打补丁，可移除 mediainit 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/mediainit），并限制可执行权限仅授予信任的管理员用户组。建议将 HP-UX 系统升级至包含该修复的后续版本（如 11.0 以上），因 10.x 系列已终止技术支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9710-071"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0541.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0497","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0497.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0300","title":"Sun Solaris NIS+ nis_cachemgr 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris NIS+ 的 nis_cachemgr 缓存管理器存在安全设计缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞向缓存中注入恶意的 NIS+ 服务器信息。当客户端查询网络信息服务时，将连接到攻击者控制的伪造服务器，导致敏感信息（如用户凭据、主机配置）被窃取或服务遭到劫持。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0300"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.247","remediation":"针对 Solaris NIS+ 的 nis_cachemgr 漏洞，建议立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #155 中提供的官方补丁。如运行 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 且无法打补丁，应在网络边界通过防火墙限制对 nis_cachemgr 端口（TCP/UDP 387）的访问，仅允许受信 NIS+ 服务器通信。由于 NIS+ 已停止维护，建议迁移至基于 LDAP 的命名服务以获得长期安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/155","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0300","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0300.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--12792e2d-cd40-4418-b42c-679d4e4e14e3.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0497.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0458","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0458.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0272","title":"Slmail POP3 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Slmail 3.0.2421 及 2.5 版本的 POP3 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标主机的 POP3 端口（默认 110）发送特制恶意数据包，导致服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成正常的邮件收发功能中断。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需复杂权限即可触发，影响运行 Slmail 服务的邮件服务器系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0272"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.843","remediation":"Slmail 产品已停止维护多年，建议迁移至现代受支持的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix、Exchange 等）。如仍需继续使用，可在防火墙层面限制 POP3 端口（110）仅允许受信任 IP 段访问，并监控异常连接流量作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0272","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/e75163879b5629a697822216993d714626893061/api/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0458.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0213","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0090","title":"IBM AIX rcp 命令本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 系统 rcp 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 rcp 命令提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存数据并获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。利用需要本地用户身份，成功利用后攻击者可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0090"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.733","remediation":"IBM 已在 AIX 4.x 版本的 APAR IY09308 中修复此漏洞，建议更新 bos.rte.net_filesystem fileset 至包含该 APAR 的维护级别。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/bin/rcp 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/rcp，或禁用 r-commands 服务（rshd、rexecd）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0090"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0490","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0490.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0295","title":"Sun Solaris sysdef 命令本地内核内存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中的 sysdef 命令存在内核内存信息泄露漏洞。本地普通用户可通过执行 sysdef 命令读取内核内存中的敏感数据，进而获取内核地址布局等关键信息，结合其他漏洞可导致权限提升至 root 级别。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.4/2.5/2.5.1 及 SunOS 5.3-5.5.1 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。Sun 已发布安全公告 157 提供修复方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0295"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin 157 提供的官方补丁。鉴于 SunOS 5.3~5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.4~2.5.1 均已停止维护，建议升级到受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11.4 或更高版本。如无法升级，临时缓解措施为：以 root 权限执行 chmod 700 /usr/sbin/sysdef 限制 sysdef 命令的访问权限，仅允许 root 用户执行，同时移除 sysdef 的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/sysdef），防止本地普通用户通过该命令读取内核内存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0490.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0368","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0368.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0185","title":"Sun SunOS/Solaris FTP 服务数据端口信任滥用远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统中 FTP 服务与 rlogin 服务之间存在信任关系绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可利用 FTP 协议的数据端口（20/tcp）主动连接至目标主机上受信任的 rlogin 服务，绕过正常认证机制实现远程命令执行。该漏洞源于 FTP 服务器被目标主机配置为信任主机，攻击者无需任何凭证即可通过构造特殊 FTP 会话获得对目标系统的完全控制，影响 SunOS 5.3~5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.3~2.5.1 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0185"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #156 提供的对应 Solaris 版本补丁。停止使用 rlogin/rsh 服务，改用 SSH 进行远程管理；删除 /etc/hosts.equiv 及所有用户的 .rhosts 文件以消除主机间隐式信任关系；配置 FTP 服务禁止 PORT 命令反弹连接至非 FTP 端口（如在 wu-ftpd 中设置 refuse-connection 规则），阻断反弹攻击路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0368.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0329","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0329.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0160","title":"Cisco IOS PPP CHAP 认证绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 设备的 PPP CHAP 认证机制存在安全绕过漏洞。远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用该漏洞建立未授权的 PPP 连接，从而获得目标网络的访问权限，可能导致敏感信息泄露、数据篡改或服务中断。该漏洞影响多款经典 Cisco IOS 设备，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互，CVSS v2 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0160"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.1 或更高版本（该漏洞已在 11.1 及后续维护版本中修复）。如无法立即升级，可在 PPP 接口配置 `access-class` ACL 限制仅允许可信源 IP 建立拨号连接，并在全局配置下使用 `no service tcp-small-servers` 和 `no service udp-small-servers` 关闭不必要的小型服务以减小攻击面。对于仍在运行不受支持老版本 IOS 的设备，建议迁移至当前受支持的 IOS 版本或替换为现代网络设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0329.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0363","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0363.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0182","title":"Samba Samba 1.9.19 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 1.9.19 及更早版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 Samba 服务发送特制的超长密码字符串触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 Samba 1.9.19 的 Unix/Linux 系统，无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0182"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.523","remediation":"立即升级 Samba 至 2.0.0 及以上版本（1.9.19 系列已停止维护，2.0.0 修复了该缓冲区溢出问题）。如无法立即升级，可在 smb.conf 中设置 hosts allow/deny 限制可访问 SMB 服务的源 IP 范围，并在防火墙层面屏蔽 TCP 端口 139 和 445 的外部访问以临时缓解风险。现代 Linux 发行版应直接使用系统包管理器更新至当前受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/h-110.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20308","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0182.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0182","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0182.nasl","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/292.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vc5j-x9w7-frw6/GHSA-vc5j-x9w7-frw6.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/jbeasl7/openvas-feed-sync-local/blob/02ed2a2b96fc19fd49a4be810f3493abb776ec4e/openvas-feeds/nvt-feed/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0182.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0363.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0470","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0282","title":"（已废弃）CVE-1999-0282 错误合并 SunOS loadmodule 两个独立漏洞的无效编号","description":"CVE-1999-0282 是一个已被官方驳回（REJECTED）的 CVE 编号，原因是它错误地将 CVE-1999-1584 和 CVE-1999-1586 两个不同漏洞的参考信息和描述合并为一条记录。NVD 已移除该编号下所有描述与引用，禁止继续使用。该编号不指向任何真实存在的漏洞，不存在可利用的攻击面或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0282"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:56.640","remediation":"CVE-1999-0282 已被撤销，请勿使用此编号。实际漏洞分别对应 CVE-1999-1584（SunOS 4.1.1–4.1.3c 及 Open Windows 3.0 中 loadmodule/modload 的本地权限提升）和 CVE-1999-1586（SunOS 4.1.x 中 xnews 调用的 loadmodule 未正确清理环境变量导致本地提权）。Sun 当时发布了补丁（如 Sun patch 100124-01），CERT 也发布了公告 CA-1993-18，但这些补丁现已无法获取。由于 SunOS 4.x 早已停止支持，建议将仍在运行的 SunOS 4.1.x 系统迁移至受支持的操作系统（如 Solaris 11、Linux 或 \\*BSD），同时严格控制 setuid/setgid 二进制文件的权限以降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0452","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0267","title":"NCSA HTTPd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.3 版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区越界写入，进而实现远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 系列版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0267"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.227","remediation":"NCSA HTTPd 已停止维护多年，建议立即迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。迁移后需重新配置虚拟主机、访问控制和 SSL 证书，并关闭旧服务器上的 80/443 端口。如无法立即迁移，可在防火墙层面限制对 80 端口的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0267","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21050","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0267.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-0267.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0267","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-0267.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0267.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-1999-0267.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0452.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0452.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0993","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0667","title":"TCP/IP ARP协议缓存投毒欺骗漏洞","description":"ARP（地址解析协议）协议设计上缺乏身份验证机制，在同一广播域内的任何攻击者均可向目标主机发送伪造的 ARP 应答报文，毒化其 ARP 缓存表，将目标 IP 地址与攻击者 MAC 地址关联。该漏洞影响所有使用 ARP 协议的网络设备，攻击者无需认证即可实施中间人攻击、IP 地址欺骗或拒绝服务攻击，是局域网中最基础且广泛存在的协议层安全问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0667"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.363","remediation":"在关键网段交换机启用动态 ARP 检测 (DAI) 和 DHCP Snooping，阻止伪造 ARP 报文；对核心资产配置静态 ARP 条目；部署 ARP 防火墙或 arpwatch 等监控工具检测异常 ARP 变化；使用 IPsec/MACsec 加密通信链路，降低中间人攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602880019797&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0192","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0192.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0079","title":"Sun Solaris 7/8 FTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7 和 Solaris 8 系统的 FTP 服务器存在资源耗尽漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送大量 PASV 命令，导致服务器可用端口被迅速耗尽，从而使合法用户无法建立新的数据连接，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用门槛低，仅需网络可达即可触发，影响运行上述 Solaris 版本的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0079"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.890","remediation":"建议安装 Sun 官方补丁 ID 106222-02 (Solaris 7) 或 106223-02 (Solaris 8)，限制单连接内 PASV 命令的并发端口数。也可在 in.ftpd 配置中降低 PASV 最小端口范围或缩短空闲端口超时。如无法升级，可在防火墙限制 FTP 控制连接速率作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0079"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0192.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0374","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0374.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0191","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 newdsn.exe 文件创建漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 的 newdsn.exe CGI 脚本存在文件创建/覆盖漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求利用此脚本，在服务器上任意创建或覆盖文件，可能导致系统配置被篡改或敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0 版本，攻击复杂度较低，无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0191"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:51.367","remediation":"立即删除 IIS 3.0 服务器上的 newdsn.exe 文件或将其所在 cgi-bin 目录权限设置为禁止匿名访问；同时升级至 IIS 4.0 或更高版本以彻底消除该 CGI 脚本，或迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并启用最新安全配置。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 过滤规则拦截对 newdsn.exe 的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/275","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20309","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c623