997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.913","remediation":"建议立即升级至 O'Reilly WebSite Professional 2.x（该版本已修复 uploader 漏洞）；如无法升级，可直接删除或禁用 webroot 下的 uploader.exe/cgi 程序，并在 Web 服务器或防火墙层面限制对 uploader 相关路径的访问。由于该产品已终止技术支持（EOL），长期解决方案是迁移至仍在安全维护期的 Web 服务器（如 Apache、Nginx 或 IIS）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0177"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0353.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0258","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0115","title":"IBM AIX bugfiler 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 3.x 操作系统中的 bugfiler 程序存在任意文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序可创建或覆盖系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 3.x 版本，攻击者仅需本地账户即可利用，无需用户交互，危害较高，CVSS 评分 7.2。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0115"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.230","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 4.1.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续发行版中修复。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/bugfiler` 移除 setuid 特权位，防止本地用户通过 bugfiler 获取 root Shell；若无需使用 bugfiler 工具，可直接 `chmod 700 /usr/bin/bugfiler` 限制仅 root 可执行。请评估是否需同时更新 `bos.rte.security` 文件集的相关安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1800","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0115","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0115.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73